00:33:32,280 --> 00:33:33,000
Thank you.

570
00:33:34,560 --> 00:33:36,755
Everyone, it's like this.

571
00:33:37,080 --> 00:33:39,320
When we left Lingnan,

572
00:33:39,480 --> 00:33:40,160
the litchis

573
00:33:40,200 --> 00:33:41,520
were still green

574
00:33:41,720 --> 00:33:43,640
so it doesn't rot on the way here.

575
00:33:44,132 --> 00:33:46,252
Now that Chang'an is near,

576
00:33:46,600 --> 00:33:48,520
we need apples to ripen it.

577
00:33:49,160 --> 00:33:50,000
Later,

578
00:33:50,240 --> 00:33:51,280
put two apples

579
00:33:51,360 --> 00:33:52,240
in each bamboo basket

580
00:33:52,680 --> 00:33:54,160
so His Majesty and the Noble Consort

581
00:33:54,280 --> 00:33:56,280
can enjoy the sweetest litchis.

582
00:33:56,333 --> 00:33:57,155
All right?

583
00:33:57,840 --> 00:33:58,480
Yes.

584
00:33:58,520 --> 00:33:59,044
Come on.

585
00:33:59,088 --> 00:34:00,155
Let's do it.

586
00:34:02,760 --> 00:34:03,600
Yan.

587
00:34:05,280 --> 00:34:05,920
I want you

588
00:34:06,520 --> 00:34:08,200
to rush to Chang'an

589
00:34:10,560 --> 00:34:13,840
and give this to the address.

590
00:34:14,400 --> 00:34:15,240
Remember.

591
00:34:15,960 --> 00:34:18,822
You must reach Chang'an before us.

592
00:34:20,120 --> 00:34:20,600
Yes.

593
00:34:21,120 --> 00:34:21,720
Gou'er!

594
00:34:22,888 --> 00:34:23,888
Look!

595
00:34:26,160 --> 00:34:26,760
Luotuo!

596
00:34:43,440 --> 00:34:45,280
Giddy up!

597
00:34:47,660 --> 00:34:54,660
(Memorial Tablet of Zheng Weifeng
and his wife, Zhang)

598
00:34:55,133 --> 00:34:57,111
When my father was in trouble back then,

599
00:34:57,288 --> 00:34:59,777
everyone in the Zheng family
only stood by and watched.

600
00:35:02,440 --> 00:35:04,160
I no longer yearn

601
00:35:06,400 --> 00:35:07,920
to return to such an arrogant family.

602
00:35:10,177 --> 00:35:11,911
When the Right Chancellor is toppled,

603
00:35:13,480 --> 00:35:14,240
I can avenge

604
00:35:14,280 --> 00:35:15,680
your spirit, Father.

605
00:35:40,200 --> 00:35:41,280
Don't worry, Zheng.

606
00:35:42,644 --> 00:35:44,355
The Left Chancellor
and the Deputy Director

607
00:35:44,422 --> 00:35:46,111
will get rid of the corrupt officials.

608
00:35:46,866 --> 00:35:49,133
However,
the Right Chancellor still holds power.

609
00:35:49,600 --> 00:35:51,360
Your identity still holds danger.

610
00:35:52,320 --> 00:35:53,688
You still need to be careful.

611
00:36:05,520 --> 00:36:06,240
Who is it?

612
00:36:12,350 --> 00:36:13,190
Please send a message.

613
00:36:13,190 --> 00:36:15,280
Zheng Ping'an is requesting
a meeting with Deputy Director Lu

614
00:36:15,288 --> 00:36:16,377
to tell him something urgent.

615
00:36:17,200 --> 00:36:17,640
Wait here.

616
00:36:20,580 --> 00:36:23,580
(First Day of June)

617
00:37:08,720 --> 00:37:10,080
Congratulations, Right Chancellor.

618
00:37:12,520 --> 00:37:14,360
I've fulfilled the request

619
00:37:14,720 --> 00:37:16,080
and brought back the litchis.

620
00:37:17,200 --> 00:37:17,840
Good.

621
00:37:18,880 --> 00:37:21,720
It's done in 11 days indeed.

622
00:37:22,400 --> 00:37:23,600
You've done well.

623
00:37:24,600 --> 00:37:25,720
Open the box and show me.

624
00:37:26,120 --> 00:37:26,760
Yes.

625
00:37:33,680 --> 00:37:34,520
It's so fresh.

626
00:37:37,200 --> 00:37:38,333
Right Chancellor.

627
00:37:38,488 --> 00:37:39,755
These are for

628
00:37:39,755 --> 00:37:41,040
His Majesty and the Noble Consort.

629
00:37:41,044 --> 00:37:42,044
Please take a look.

630
00:37:45,040 --> 00:37:45,920
Good.

631
00:37:47,280 --> 00:37:49,480
The gifts to Tang

632
00:37:49,600 --> 00:37:51,760
by other nations

633
00:37:52,200 --> 00:37:53,600
might be surpassed

634
00:37:53,680 --> 00:37:54,600
by these

635
00:37:54,680 --> 00:37:55,840
small, fresh litchis.

636
00:37:55,840 --> 00:37:57,400
Exactly!

637
00:37:57,680 --> 00:37:58,240
Wonderful!

638
00:37:58,720 --> 00:37:59,777
Cover the box.

639
00:38:00,822 --> 00:38:03,120
Both of you have done well
in transporting the litchis.

640
00:38:03,640 --> 00:38:05,894
I've asked His Majesty

641
00:38:06,160 --> 00:38:08,640
to invite both of you
to attend the banquet.

642
00:38:10,000 --> 00:38:11,244
Thank His Majesty.

643
00:38:11,280 --> 00:38:12,533
Thank you, Right Chancellor.

644
00:38:12,600 --> 00:38:14,450
Thank you for your blessing,
Right Chancellor.

645
00:38:14,600 --> 00:38:16,400
I've been rushing here for days

646
00:38:16,440 --> 00:38:17,400
and isn't well-groomed.

647
00:38:17,511 --> 00:38:19,933
I'm afraid it might
scare His Majesty and the Noble Consort.

648
00:38:20,000 --> 00:38:21,160
It's fine.

649
00:38:22,120 --> 00:38:26,480
Looking like this shows your loyalty.

650
00:38:26,960 --> 00:38:28,160
Am I right, Inspector Yu?

651
00:38:28,760 --> 00:38:30,080
You are correct, Right Chancellor.

652
00:38:31,400 --> 00:38:31,760
Come.

653
00:38:31,800 --> 00:38:32,760
Get up.

654
00:38:32,888 --> 00:38:34,533
Thank you, Right Chancellor.

655
00:38:46,840 --> 00:38:49,880
(The Consort Noble knows
His Majesty doesn't like lavishness)

656
00:38:50,240 --> 00:38:53,040
(and asks for this year's birthday)

657
00:38:53,040 --> 00:38:55,640
(to be as simple as possible.)

658
00:38:56,266 --> 00:38:58,222
(The purpose
is just to enjoy the flowers.)

659
00:38:59,200 --> 00:39:00,600
(Flowers are pretty)

660
00:39:01,000 --> 00:39:03,880
(but they are precious
because someone appreciates them.)

661
00:39:04,320 --> 00:39:06,720
(It is a blessing for the kingdom)

662
00:39:07,080 --> 00:39:08,880
(and its people.)

663
00:39:33,920 --> 00:39:35,400
Mr. Li, take a look.

664
00:39:35,680 --> 00:39:37,160
I'm sure you don't recognize

665
00:39:37,720 --> 00:39:38,880
the Leyou Garden today.

666
00:39:48,360 --> 00:39:51,560
It has been utterly transformed.

667
00:39:53,560 --> 00:39:54,440
Mr. Li.

668
00:39:55,444 --> 00:39:57,120
That's not the right way to describe it.

669
00:39:57,840 --> 00:39:59,960
The Right Chancellor has exquisite taste

670
00:40:00,400 --> 00:40:01,360
and has decorated

671
00:40:01,480 --> 00:40:03,160
the Leyou Garden to be so magnificent.

672
00:40:03,600 --> 00:40:05,400
The Noble Consort's birthday banquet

673
00:40:05,640 --> 00:40:06,680
will surely be an event

674
00:40:06,760 --> 00:40:09,160
that the people
will talk about for ages.

675
00:40:13,480 --> 00:40:14,320
Right Chancellor,

676
00:40:14,439 --> 00:40:15,639
His Majesty has left the palace

677
00:40:15,720 --> 00:40:16,880
and is coming to Leyou Garden.

678
00:40:17,120 --> 00:40:18,080
He will be here soon.

679
00:40:18,720 --> 00:40:19,400
Good.

680
00:40:24,960 --> 00:40:25,760
Right Chancellor,

681
00:40:26,800 --> 00:40:28,040
can I

682
00:40:28,560 --> 00:40:30,080
ask you a question?

683
00:40:30,760 --> 00:40:31,880
Mr. Li,

684
00:40:32,840 --> 00:40:35,320
you are a hardworking person.

685
00:40:36,720 --> 00:40:38,040
At my place,

686
00:40:39,120 --> 00:40:41,680
people who are capable like him

687
00:40:42,520 --> 00:40:44,040
will never be neglected.

688
00:40:45,320 --> 00:40:46,680
Look at the fresh litchis.

689
00:40:47,120 --> 00:40:49,400
It must be made into a yearly event.

690
00:40:49,800 --> 00:40:50,520
In the future,

691
00:40:50,977 --> 00:40:53,280
you are still the Litchi Envoy.

692
00:40:53,600 --> 00:40:55,177
Later,
I'll ask the Ministry of Personnel

693
00:40:55,177 --> 00:40:56,666
to transfer you to the Carriage Bureau.

694
00:40:56,800 --> 00:40:58,840
You'll be promoted in the future.

695
00:40:59,600 --> 00:41:00,560
Be patient.

696
00:41:00,920 --> 00:41:02,720
Good days are coming for you.

697
00:41:04,040 --> 00:41:06,480
That's not what I want to ask about.

698
00:41:08,000 --> 00:41:10,880
A lot of money is spent
on litchi transportation.

699
00:41:11,840 --> 00:41:14,800
Money might not be my concern

700
00:41:14,800 --> 00:41:16,880
but I still feel worried.

701
00:41:18,040 --> 00:41:20,400
Please explain the situation to me.

702
00:41:20,900 --> 00:41:22,160
His Majesty and the Noble Consort

703
00:41:22,200 --> 00:41:23,080
are arriving soon.

704
00:41:23,960 --> 00:41:25,640
Must you ask me

705
00:41:25,640 --> 00:41:27,160
to explain it to you right now?

706
00:41:27,400 --> 00:41:27,880
Exactly.

707
00:41:29,440 --> 00:41:30,720
Transportation of litchi

708
00:41:31,160 --> 00:41:34,640
has used up 20,000 guan.

709
00:41:34,880 --> 00:41:36,160
The average cost

710
00:41:36,200 --> 00:41:38,120
to transport one litchi
from Lingnan to Chang'an

711
00:41:38,640 --> 00:41:40,320
is 100 guan.

712
00:41:40,920 --> 00:41:42,080
100 guan

713
00:41:42,200 --> 00:41:43,960
is ten years' worth of income

714
00:41:44,640 --> 00:41:46,000
for a normal family.

715
00:41:46,720 --> 00:41:47,400
That means

716
00:41:47,760 --> 00:41:49,480
every litchi

717
00:41:49,680 --> 00:41:50,520
eaten by a noble

718
00:41:50,520 --> 00:41:51,960
on this banquet here

719
00:41:52,120 --> 00:41:53,960
costs a year's worth of income

720
00:41:54,040 --> 00:41:56,280
for ten families.

721
00:41:58,080 --> 00:42:00,000
Where does the money come from?

722
00:42:01,440 --> 00:42:02,480
I saw the money

723
00:42:02,840 --> 00:42:05,520
being extorted
from Lingnan's litchi gardens,

724
00:42:05,640 --> 00:42:07,680
and the residences on the way here.

725
00:42:07,800 --> 00:42:09,400
The money was extracted

726
00:42:09,480 --> 00:42:11,200
from the people of Tang.

727
00:42:12,400 --> 00:42:15,320
As a chancellor, one should govern

728
00:42:15,440 --> 00:42:16,533
and balance all matters.

729
00:42:16,760 --> 00:42:17,920
How do you balance

730
00:42:17,960 --> 00:42:20,760
the importance of litchis
and the kingdom, Right Chancellor?

731
00:42:21,080 --> 00:42:22,160
Which is more important

732
00:42:22,680 --> 00:42:25,200
to His Majesty?

733
00:42:25,880 --> 00:42:27,800
I told you

734
00:42:28,088 --> 00:42:30,240
about the good and bad
of litchi transportation.

735
00:42:31,160 --> 00:42:32,360
Why are you asking

736
00:42:32,440 --> 00:42:33,488
such a muddled question?

737
00:42:33,533 --> 00:42:35,000
I've never been so enlightened.

738
00:42:35,780 --> 00:42:38,740
=The Litchi Road=

739
00:42:40,880 --> 00:42:42,280
Kill Li Shande.

740
00:42:48,120 --> 00:42:49,840
As long as Your Majesty

741
00:42:50,200 --> 00:42:51,480
and the Noble Consort are happy,

742
00:42:51,760 --> 00:42:55,000
I will be satisfied.

743
00:42:57,160 --> 00:42:58,160
Someone saw Li Shande

744
00:42:58,280 --> 00:43:00,040
taking his daughter and leaving the city

745
00:43:00,080 --> 00:43:01,577
through Qixia Gate.

746
00:43:11,440 --> 00:43:18,760
♪The Han emperor
longed for a beauty to rival a nation♪

747
00:43:23,420 --> 00:43:28,770
♪For years he ruled,
yet couldn't find one♪

748
00:43:34,660 --> 00:43:38,110
♪A girl from the Yang family
came of age♪

749
00:43:38,270 --> 00:43:41,780
♪Raised in her chamber,
unknown to the world♪

750
00:43:41,940 --> 00:43:45,600
♪Born with stunning grace
she couldn't hide♪

751
00:43:45,700 --> 00:43:49,320
♪One day,
she was chosen to serve by his side♪

752
00:43:56,660 --> 00:44:01,940
♪She glanced back
with a smile of myriad charms♪

753
00:44:01,940 --> 00:44:07,380
♪All the palace beauties
lost their glow♪

754
00:44:13,100 --> 00:44:16,790
♪In the chilly spring,
she bathed at Huaqing Pond♪

755
00:44:16,790 --> 00:44:20,780
♪The warm spring water
slid over her silky skin♪

756
00:44:23,990 --> 00:44:27,710
♪Handmaids helped her
rise from the water♪

757
00:44:27,710 --> 00:44:31,860
♪Thus began the time
she gained the emperor's favor♪

758
00:44:34,980 --> 00:44:38,600
♪Flowing hair, a flower-bright face,
and a hairpin of glamour♪

759
00:44:38,600 --> 00:44:42,410
♪In the warm lotus canopy,
they spent spring nights together♪

760
00:44:44,130 --> 00:44:47,930
♪Those sweet nights were too short,
he rose until noon♪

761
00:44:47,930 --> 00:44:53,740
♪From then on,
he skipped the morning court♪

762
00:45:00,720 --> 00:45:04,380
♪Always at his side,
forever delighting and dining♪

763
00:45:04,380 --> 00:45:07,910
♪They spent spring on spring outings,
night on night together♪

764
00:45:08,080 --> 00:45:13,860
♪In the palace
lived three thousand beauties♪

765
00:45:15,240 --> 00:45:20,340
♪Yet all three thousand favors
were hers alone♪
